            <title>[LU-4333] ZFS test failure recovery-small test_29a: import is not in FULL state</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4333</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Nathaniel Clark &amp;lt;nathaniel.l.clark@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite runs:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/4db1547c-4f74-11e3-84d3-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/4db1547c-4f74-11e3-84d3-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/ce33eb18-5970-11e3-9707-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/ce33eb18-5970-11e3-9707-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/7c71e1ac-5869-11e3-b1ae-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/7c71e1ac-5869-11e3-b1ae-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/75efe67a-596e-11e3-83d7-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/75efe67a-596e-11e3-83d7-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_29a failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;import is not in FULL state&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: recovery-small 29a&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This appears to have the same symptoms as &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3143&quot; title=&quot;recovery-small test_29a: FAIL: import is not in FULL state&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-3143&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-3143&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; but is ZFS only.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
